FEATURES

EVERYTHING YOU NEED IN ONE STUDY APP

Notes, documents, AI tutoring, quizzes, and progress tracking all live inside one app. No more jumping between five tools to get through a problem set.

PROACTIVE AI TUTORING

Reef reads your handwriting and delivers feedback during natural pauses. No prompts needed.

HANDWRITING RECOGNITION

Write math, chemistry, or prose with Apple Pencil. Reef transcribes instantly.

ALL YOUR MATERIALS IN ONE PLACE
